modules.description: Provides functions for producing and consuming messages from Apache Kafka topics, including message serialization, delivery guarantees, and offset management. Operates with byte sequences, message headers, and Kafka-specific error codes. Used to integrate real-time data pipelines, log aggregation, and event sourcing systems.

Provides functions to consume individual or batched messages from Kafka topics or queues with timeout control, and to create and manage producers that send messages with optional key support. Operates on Kafka topics, partitions, queues, and message structures. Used for real-time data ingestion, batch processing, and ensuring message delivery in event-driven systems.
